#{wandershot_text} is designed to be a simple to use, minimalistic, and beautiful app for travel blogging.

The following guidelines should be followed when updating the site or adding new posts:

%ul
  %li
    Each post should have a large striking picture to accompany it
  %li
    Each post should have a date and a location to build a timeline
  %li
    The user interface should be minimal and unobtrusive; the focus is on the text and images
